01:10.916 --> 01:13.166
Father's looking for you, Bogdana.

01:13.374 --> 01:14.666
Don't get caught.

01:15.707 --> 01:17.624
Where are you headed, Darinka?

01:17.832 --> 01:21.416
I'm going to the fields
to bring Fyodor his supper.

01:21.624 --> 01:23.749
Don't stay out too late, sister.

01:23.957 --> 01:25.166
I'll try my best.

01:25.624 --> 01:26.707
You'd better!

01:26.916 --> 01:28.499
Oh, who's talking!

01:28.707 --> 01:29.916
Bogdana!

01:30.124 --> 01:32.416
- Where the hell are you?
- I must run.

01:35.041 --> 01:37.374
Who's that looking for trouble?

01:37.582 --> 01:41.166
I'll show him trouble, the scoundrel!

01:43.166 --> 01:44.749
