Her ears were bigger than that.

05:19.624 --> 05:23.082
What do you
think this means, Mr. Gogol?

05:24.832 --> 05:26.499
"Twelve plus one..."

05:27.874 --> 05:30.332
Perhaps there's
some kind of system.

05:30.791 --> 05:34.916
Look, here are the four dates
when the horseman killed,

05:35.124 --> 05:36.457
and one more date:

05:37.207 --> 05:38.874
October 2.

05:39.332 --> 05:42.291
October 2
is the day after tomorrow.

05:43.916 --> 05:48.749
Guro died before Paraska,
but identified the date of her murder.

05:48.957 --> 05:51.082
So, judging by his calculations,

05:51.291 --> 05:55.791
the next murder
should take place on October 2.

05:58.166 --> 05:59.582
Why that date?

06:00.374 --> 06:03.791
October 2 is
the feast of the Intercession.

06:07.166 --> 06:10.791
CASE FILE: NIKOLAI GOGOL
