17:50.374 --> 17:51.666
Mr. Gogol...

17:52.916 --> 17:54.041
Are you well?

17:55.749 --> 17:58.124
Yes, yes, I'm fine.

17:59.499 --> 18:00.832
HEY, everyone!

18:11.207 --> 18:13.832
God rest her innocent soul.

18:14.041 --> 18:15.249
