22:42.249 --> 22:47.207
and only Gogol,
the most sickly child, remained alive.

22:49.332 --> 22:51.166
"The mystery of birth".

22:52.291 --> 22:53.249
"A dark one?"

23:02.832 --> 23:04.666
You can enter this world.

23:06.374 --> 23:07.374
It is your gift.

24:03.999 --> 24:06.082
The blood of innocents,

